      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>spiced tomato paste</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>spiced tomato paste </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook, covered, for 15-20 min or until the squash is fork-tender and the sauce has reduced slightly</p>",
