    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Once the sauce has reduced, add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>sweetcorn</strong> to the pan and stir it all together – this is your <strong>spiced butternut squash & sweetcorn</strong></p>",
